{"tid":197983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情境題:如果<宋少帝>同佢地十萬軍隊係香港復活 港共警察會有咩反應?","createTime":"2017-04-12T08:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T08:26:54.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab09fe5ea75276cab20c495bf742d65e222a46f","tid":197983,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:23:34.000Z","msg":"宋恭帝德祐二年正月十八日（1276年2月4日）<br />\n一心想對宋朝皇室斬草除根的元軍統帥伯顏，對宋端宗的南宋流亡小朝廷窮追不捨。景炎三年（1278年），宋端宗崩，以至軍心渙散，無心戀戰。當時陸秀夫在碙州梅蔚（即今日<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>香港大嶼山梅窩</ins></span>），改碙州為祥龍縣，擁立趙昺為皇帝，改元「祥興」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情境題:如果&lt;宋少帝&gt;同佢地十萬軍隊，突然係香港復活 港共警察會有咩反應?<br />\n<br />\n會否立即歸順?"},{"pid":"cabe2be207f6dff1ec50fbc2f5ff47229fc270fa","tid":197983,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/b0d0000eb1504670023\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fb0d0000eb1504670023&h=8210c635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"591f4709faa3cd13d7a0c143d702925c153dff0e","tid":197983,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/ac80003309ae52bb8eb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fac80003309ae52bb8eb&h=72edbede&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}